::Fliq::

Fliq looks down for a second, stepping back. Iron Raptor was 
obviously not happy that Strafe wasn't enjoying the inside of a cell 
right now.

"You told me to put him in the brig, ma'am," he replies to her 
question, "But that plan didn't take into consideration the CR 
failing to keep him out of action and him nearly strangling me."
